- node: clear state new way since pcmk 1.1.8 (bnc#843699)
- Integrate hb_report as part of crmsh

* Tue Sep 24 2013 Kristoffer Grnlund <kgronlund@suse.com>, Dejan Muhamedagic <dejan@suse.de>, and many others
